import React from 'react';
import Header from '../components/Header';
import { Button, Container, Form} from 'react-bootstrap';
import './ProductList.css';

const AddProduct = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Header/>
            <Container className="input-container">
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Name</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter name" onchanget />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Description</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter description" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Quantity</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Enter quantity" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group aria-required>
                        <Form.Label>Price</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Enter price" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.File id="exampleFormControlFile1" label="Image of product" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                        Add
                    </Button>
                </Form>
            </Container>
        </>
    );
};

export default AddProduct;
